<HEADLINE>
<P>
BASEBALL / DAILY REPORT; AROUND THE MAJORS; JORDAN EXTENDS HITTING STREAK TO 11 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Michael Jordan went one for four with a single, extending his hitting streak 
to 11 games, in the Birmingham Barons' 5-3 loss to the Nashville Xpress. Jordan 
is 15 for 46 and is batting .326. 
</P>
</TEXT>
