LAGUNA NIGUEL SURFER IS SECOND AT PISMO BEACH 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Pat O'Connell of Laguna Niguel finished second Sunday at the Body Glove Bud 
Surf Tour stop in Pismo Beach. 
</P>
<P>
 Chris Brown of Santa Barbara won the event and $4,000. O'Connell won $2,000. 
Taylor Knox of Carlsbad was third, Rob Machado of Cardiff was fourth and Vince 
De La Pena of Laguna Niguel was fifth. 
</P>
<P>
 Ted Robinson of Manhattan Beach won the longboarding competition and Josh 
Baxter of San Clemente was second. 
</P>
