<HEADLINE>
<P>
COMING TUESDAY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 THE TIMES 100: Tuesday's Business section will include the seventh annual 
Times 100 report, which looks at California's best-performing publicly held 
companies. The section charts the performance of more than 600 companies by 
profits, sales, growth, market value, employment and other factors in 1993. 
</P>
