<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEW LIFE & STYLE SECTION DEBUTS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Beginning today, The Times introduces Life & Style, a new section that 
reflects the vibrancy and vitality of Southern California. Life & Style will 
feature daily theme pages focusing on relationships, health and fitness, 
families, fashion and design, and consumer issues. The new section replaces 
View, but all the regular features -- such as Dear Abby, Ann Landers and the 
horoscope -- remain. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
